OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772499776
OL,3,CBus drivers strike 'will continue' on
OL,4,CFriday if 'serious proposal' is not
OL,5,Cmade
OL,7,FThe union representing bus drivers on
OL,8,Fthe Isle of Man says the strike 'will
OL,9,Fresume' on Friday, if a 'serious
OL,10,Fproposal' is not presented by the Isle
OL,11,Fof Man Government.
OL,13,FUnite the Union met with the
OL,14,FDepartment of Infrastructure on
OL,15,FTuesday 24 February, but failed to
OL,16,Freach an agreement over pay and
OL,17,Fworking conditions.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
