FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772499776
OL,3,CBus drivers strike 'will continue' on
OL,4,CFriday if 'serious proposal' is not
OL,5,Cmade
OL,7,FBus Vannin drivers temporarily
OL,8,Freturned to work on Tuesday 3 March
OL,9,Fafter a 10-day walkout, which the
OL,10,Funion described as 'three clear days
OL,11,Fbefore industrial action resumes'.
OL,13,FA spokesperson for the union said:
OL,14,F'The last offer reduced the previously
OL,15,Fdiscussed #16.88 rate to #16.84 per
OL,16,Fhour and replaced proper consolidated
OL,17,Fpay with a #1,000 non-pensionable
OL,18,Fpayment for full-time staff.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772499776
OL,3,CBus drivers strike 'will continue' on
OL,4,CFriday if 'serious proposal' is not
OL,5,Cmade
OL,7,F'Part-time drivers receive less.
OL,8,FCasual drivers receive nothing. The
OL,9,Ftwo-tier structure remains.
OL,11,F'Drivers are working 40`45 hours a
OL,12,Fweek. This dispute is about fair,
OL,13,Fconsolidated and pensionable pay - and
OL,14,Fabout creating a harmonious,
OL,15,Ftransparent system that treats all
OL,16,Fdrivers equally. That is something our
OL,17,Fmembers feel strongly about.'
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
