OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772499776
OL,3,CBus drivers strike 'will continue' on
OL,4,CFriday if 'serious proposal' is not
OL,5,Cmade
OL,7,FFurther strike dates have been
OL,8,Fannounced for every weekend in March
OL,9,Ffrom Fridays to Mondays, with the next
OL,10,Fstrike running between Friday 6 March
OL,11,Fand Monday 9 March.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
